WEBVTT

00:09.040 --> 00:10.410
<b>Whoa!</b>

00:10.410 --> 00:13.620
<b>I-It's an earth dragon!</b>

00:23.090 --> 00:25.340
<b>The earth dragon. A first-class Danger Beast.</b>

00:25.720 --> 00:27.680
<b>A worthy opponent indeed.</b>

00:33.520 --> 00:34.440
<b>You sound upset.</b>

00:36.650 --> 00:37.650
<b>It's over.</b>

00:53.500 --> 00:55.080
<b>That was amazing!</b>

00:55.080 --> 00:58.500
<b>You single-handedly took down a Danger Beast!</b>

00:59.790 --> 01:01.250
<b>Of course!</b>

01:01.250 --> 01:04.340
<b>That thing was no match for me. It was child's play!</b>

01:04.340 --> 01:06.680
<b>By the way, I'm Tatsumi.</b>

01:06.680 --> 01:10.760
<b>One day, everyone in the imperial capital's gonna know my name, so you'd better remember it.</b>

01:10.760 --> 01:14.390
<b>You're saying you want to make it big in the capital?</b>

01:14.390 --> 01:15.390
<b>Yeah!</b>

01:15.390 --> 01:18.520
<b>Every country boy dreams of winning success and fame in the big city!</b>

01:18.520 --> 01:22.230
<b>The imperial capital isn't the place of hopes and dreams that you think it is.</b>

01:22.570 --> 01:24.150
<b>It's definitely lively,</b>

01:24.150 --> 01:27.490
<b>but it's home to monsters even worse than that earth dragon.</b>

01:27.490 --> 01:28.490
<b>What?</b>

01:28.490 --> 01:30.650
<b>You mean there are Danger Beasts in the city, too?</b>

01:30.870 --> 01:32.160
<b>I mean the people.</b>

01:32.160 --> 01:34.030
<b>They may be humans, 
but their hearts are monstrous.</b>

01:34.500 --> 01:36.620
<b>The capital's crawling with them.</b>

01:37.710 --> 01:39.450
<b>I appreciate your advice,</b>

01:39.740 --> 01:42.090
<b>but I can't turn back now.{xythar to vivid after picking up akame ga kill}</b>

01:42.460 --> 01:43.210
<b>I...</b>

01:43.210 --> 01:44.090
<b>No, we...</b>

01:44.630 --> 01:47.760
<b>We're gonna make it in the imperial capital 
and save our village!</b>

01:50.800 --> 01:53.560
<b><i>Just as humans eventually rot away,</i></b>

01:53.560 --> 01:55.600
<b><i>nations also decay and collapse.</i></b>

01:56.640 --> 01:59.270
<b><i>Even the imperial capital, which has prospered for a thousand years,</i></b>

01:59.270 --> 02:02.190
<b><i>is now a living hell of corruption.</i></b>

02:02.190 --> 02:04.900
<b><i>Wicked spirits in human form run amok,</i></b>

02:04.900 --> 02:07.240
<b><i>claiming everything as their own.</i></b>

02:09.160 --> 02:11.990
<b><i>And those evils which heaven cannot judge</i></b>

02:11.990 --> 02:14.040
<b><i>will be dealt with in the shadows.{you could say they're... judged in darkness}</i></b>

02:15.160 --> 02:17.210
<b><i>By us:</i></b>

02:17.210 --> 02:18.540
<b><i>the assassins.</i></b>

