<b>So this is the imperial capital!</b>

03:59.260 --> 04:02.260
<b>If I make good money here, 
I could buy the entire village!</b>

04:02.260 --> 04:04.390
<b>I should head for the barracks.</b>

04:06.470 --> 04:07.680
<b>Oh...</b>

04:07.680 --> 04:09.770
<b>You're an applicant too, huh?</b>

04:09.770 --> 04:12.440
<b>Fill out this form, and bring it back to me.</b>

04:12.440 --> 04:13.810
<b>This means...</b>

04:14.310 --> 04:16.860
<b>I'll be starting out as a grunt?</b>

04:16.860 --> 04:17.690
<b>Obviously.</b>

04:17.690 --> 04:19.980
<b>Who has time for that?!</b>

04:19.980 --> 04:21.940
<b>Just look at my technique.</b>

04:21.940 --> 04:25.160
<b>If I show promise, will you start me out as a commanding officer?</b>

04:25.160 --> 04:26.280
<b>Get out!</b>

04:27.620 --> 04:28.620
<b>What the hell?</b>

04:28.620 --> 04:29.830
<b>At least give me a chance!</b>

04:29.830 --> 04:30.830
<b>Don't be ridiculous!</b>

04:30.830 --> 04:32.870
<b>We've had no end of applicants in this recession!</b>

04:32.870 --> 04:35.710
<b>You think we can hire anyone 
who strolls through the door?!</b>

04:35.710 --> 04:37.040
<b>Oh, really?</b>

04:37.040 --> 04:39.550
<b>Got it? Then scram, you damned brat!</b>

04:43.720 --> 04:46.760
<b><i>Do I cause a scene and make a name for myself?</i></b>

04:46.760 --> 04:48.760
<b><i>But what if I get arrested?</i></b>

04:48.760 --> 04:50.140
<b>Hi!</b>

04:50.850 --> 04:51.890
<b>Hmm?</b>

04:52.310 --> 04:54.850
<b>You seem troubled, young man.</b>

04:54.850 --> 04:56.730
<b>Sounds like you need a lady's assistance.</b>

04:57.980 --> 05:01.150
<b>Th-The capital's even bigger than I thought!</b>

05:02.740 --> 05:03.860
<b>What're you looking at?</b>

05:05.490 --> 05:09.830
<b>I guess you came all the way from the country, dreaming of making it in the big city?</b>

05:09.830 --> 05:11.160
<b>How'd you know that?</b>

05:11.160 --> 05:12.830
<b>I could tell the moment I saw you.</b>

05:12.830 --> 05:15.460
<b>Anyone who's lived here long enough can spot outsiders instantly.</b>

05:15.460 --> 05:15.920
<b>Anyway...</b>

05:16.580 --> 05:19.960
<b>I know a much quicker way to get government work.</b>

05:19.960 --> 05:20.840
<b>Seriously?</b>

05:20.840 --> 05:21.880
<b>Wanna know how?</b>

05:21.880 --> 05:23.090
<b>Mm-hm!</b>

05:23.460 --> 05:26.050
<b>Then you can treat me to lunch!</b>

05:29.760 --> 05:33.640
<b>Nothing beats an afternoon drink!</b>

05:34.140 --> 05:35.560
<b>How 'bout a glass, young man?</b>

05:35.560 --> 05:36.390
<b>Let's have some fun!</b>

05:36.390 --> 05:38.940
<b>Just tell me how to get hired by the government!</b>

05:39.270 --> 05:41.690
<b>Right. In short, you need two things.</b>

05:43.110 --> 05:44.900
<b>Connections and money.</b>

05:44.900 --> 05:46.900
<b>M-Money?</b>

05:46.900 --> 05:49.410
<b>There's a guy I know in the military.</b>

05:49.410 --> 05:52.200
<b>If I grease his palm with some cash, 
you'll be hired right away!</b>

05:53.450 --> 05:54.870
<b>I get it.</b>

05:54.870 --> 05:55.870
<b>Then...</b>

05:55.870 --> 05:57.330
<b>Would this be enough?</b>

05:57.330 --> 05:59.080
<b>Oh, absolutely!</b>

05:59.080 --> 06:02.590
<b>On my way here, I collected some rewards 
for slaying Danger Beasts.</b>

06:03.750 --> 06:05.050
<b>So you're strong.</b>

06:05.510 --> 06:07.380
<b>You'll be a commanding officer in no time!</b>

06:07.380 --> 06:09.010
<b>Sounds great! I'll leave it to you!</b>

06:10.970 --> 06:14.770
<b>I'm glad we were able to meet. 
I know you'll learn a lot from the experience.{heh}</b>

06:14.770 --> 06:18.060
<b>Just sit tight while I take care of everything, okay?</b>

06:18.060 --> 06:19.980
<b>Okay!</b>

06:31.370 --> 06:33.870
<b>Sir, it's almost closing time.</b>

06:33.870 --> 06:36.330
<b>Oh, I'm waiting for someone.</b>

06:36.330 --> 06:39.540
<b>Sorry to break it to you, but you've been had.</b>

06:40.210 --> 06:40.880
<b>Huh?</b>

06:41.500 --> 06:42.960
<b>Huh?!</b>

06:42.960 --> 06:46.010
<b>Times are tough, you know. Were you born yesterday?</b>

06:46.010 --> 06:47.720
<b>Th-That's fraud!</b>

06:47.720 --> 06:48.380
<b>I'm reporting her!</b>

06:48.380 --> 06:49.630
<b>Don't bother.</b>

06:49.630 --> 06:51.930
<b>If anything, it's your fault for being so easily tricked.</b>

06:54.510 --> 06:56.100
<b>Damn it!</b>

06:56.100 --> 06:58.480
<b>After paying off the tab, I'm flat broke!</b>

06:58.480 --> 06:59.690
<b>Damn those boobs!</b>

06:59.690 --> 07:01.810
<b>I mean, damn that woman!</b>

07:01.810 --> 07:04.190
<b>Is this what you meant by 
learning from the experience?</b>

07:05.780 --> 07:07.030
<b>Damn it.</b>

07:07.030 --> 07:09.900
<b>No one out in the country would lie like that.</b>

07:11.660 --> 07:12.870
<b>Oh well.</b>

07:13.240 --> 07:14.780
<b>Guess I'm spending the night outside.</b>

07:14.780 --> 07:16.240
<b>I can sleep anywhere.</b>

07:16.990 --> 07:17.750
<b>Stop.</b>

07:21.580 --> 07:23.460
<b>Again, my lady?</b>

07:23.460 --> 07:24.710
<b>You know I can't help it.</b>

07:24.710 --> 07:26.420
<b>It's my nature.</b>

