07:34.600 --> 07:36.720
<b>I don't have any money.</b>

07:37.770 --> 07:40.060
<b>You wouldn't be sleeping here if you did, would you?</b>

07:40.060 --> 07:43.650
<b>Lady Aria can't ignore people like you.</b>

07:43.650 --> 07:45.610
<b>You should accept her generosity.</b>

07:45.610 --> 07:46.570
<b>What would you like to do?</b>

07:47.980 --> 07:49.110
<b>Well...</b>

07:49.110 --> 07:51.320
<b>I guess it's better than sleeping outside.</b>

07:51.530 --> 07:53.280
<b>It's settled, then!</b>

07:53.280 --> 07:54.030
<b>Oh...</b>

07:54.030 --> 07:56.240
<b>Aria's brought someone home again.</b>

07:56.240 --> 07:56.870
<b>My...</b>

07:56.870 --> 07:58.120
<b>It's a real habit of hers.</b>

07:58.120 --> 07:59.200
<b>I wonder how many this makes.</b>

07:59.500 --> 08:00.830
<b>Mother!</b>

08:00.830 --> 08:03.460
<b>Th-Thank you.</b>

08:04.170 --> 08:07.130
<b><i>Those guards look really strong.</i></b>

08:05.080 --> 08:06.670
<b>There's no need to be nervous.</b>

08:07.130 --> 08:08.840
<b><i>Maybe that's why the people here</i></b>

08:07.130 --> 08:08.840
<b>I bet you're hungry.</b>

08:08.840 --> 08:11.880
<b><i>can show kindness to a stranger without feeling threatened.</i></b>

08:13.220 --> 08:17.850
<b><i>It's nice to know that even the capital 
still has people with goodness in their hearts.</i></b>

08:17.850 --> 08:20.310
<b>Thank you very much for taking me in!</b>

08:26.940 --> 08:28.190
<b>I see.</b>

08:28.440 --> 08:31.690
<b>You seek a successful military career so you can save your village.</b>

08:31.690 --> 08:32.400
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

08:33.070 --> 08:34.110
<b>However...</b>

08:34.530 --> 08:36.870
<b>It's peaceful here within the capital,</b>

08:36.870 --> 08:40.660
<b>but the homelands of three other races surround this country.</b>

08:40.660 --> 08:44.830
<b>You could be sent to fight on the borders.</b>

08:45.500 --> 08:46.880
<b>I'm fully prepared for that.</b>

08:47.080 --> 08:48.340
<b>I see.</b>

08:48.340 --> 08:49.750
<b>Your determination is impressive.</b>

08:49.750 --> 08:51.920
<b>A splendid example of youth.</b>

08:51.920 --> 08:54.300
<b>Did you come from the village all by yourself, Tatsumi?</b>

08:54.300 --> 08:55.840
<b>No. There were three of us.</b>

08:56.390 --> 08:57.550
<b>The thing is...</b>

09:01.970 --> 09:04.100
<b>All right! We'll be on our way, Chief!</b>

09:04.100 --> 09:04.850
<b>Right.</b>

09:04.850 --> 09:08.020
<b>You three have always complemented each other's strengths.</b>

09:08.020 --> 09:11.070
<b>Use your skills to rise through the ranks.</b>

09:11.070 --> 09:12.190
<b>Leave it to us.</b>

09:12.190 --> 09:13.940
<b>We'll bring wealth to the village.</b>

09:13.940 --> 09:16.860
<b>And then no one will have to starve!</b>

09:16.860 --> 09:21.450
<b>Though it'll probably take ten years for me, the great Ieyasu, to become famous.</b>

09:21.450 --> 09:24.830
<b>The great Ieyasu will probably get his head chopped off for breaking the law.</b>

09:24.830 --> 09:26.080
<b>Damn it, Sayo!</b>

09:26.080 --> 09:27.880
<b>You're gonna jinx me here!</b>

09:27.880 --> 09:32.170
<b>You'll only have yourself to blame!</b>

09:27.880 --> 09:30.380
<b>It seems you all have plenty of energy.</b>

09:30.920 --> 09:32.170
<b>Now, Tatsumi...</b>

09:32.170 --> 09:33.460
<b>My last parting gift for you.</b>

09:33.960 --> 09:35.470
<b>Take this.</b>

09:36.260 --> 09:37.510
<b>When in need...</b>

09:37.510 --> 09:38.300
<b>Sell it, right?</b>

09:38.300 --> 09:39.260
<b>No!</b>

09:40.720 --> 09:42.680
<b>Keep it close to you,</b>

09:43.140 --> 09:45.560
<b>and God will surely help you.</b>

09:46.520 --> 09:47.390
<b>Yeah.</b>

09:47.390 --> 09:49.110
<b>Thank you, Chief!</b>

09:50.310 --> 09:52.980
<b>And so, we left in high spirits.</b>

09:53.530 --> 09:55.240
<b>But soon after, we got attacked by bandits,</b>

09:55.240 --> 09:56.990
<b>and we've been separated ever since.</b>

09:56.990 --> 09:57.860
<b>Oh dear.</b>

09:58.240 --> 10:01.830
<b>Those two are strong fighters, 
so I'm not necessarily worried, but...</b>

10:01.830 --> 10:04.870
<b>Ieyasu has absolutely no sense of direction.</b>

10:04.870 --> 10:06.250
<b>What was that?!</b>

10:06.250 --> 10:09.830
<b>I wonder if he'll even be able to make it to our meeting place.</b>

10:09.830 --> 10:10.840
<b>Very well, then.</b>

10:10.840 --> 10:11.460
<b>Huh?</b>

10:11.460 --> 10:13.840
<b>I'll put in a good word with a 
military acquaintance of mine.</b>

10:14.510 --> 10:16.920
<b>And I'll request a search for those two, as well.</b>

10:17.680 --> 10:18.630
<b>Really?</b>

10:19.550 --> 10:20.970
<b>Thank you so much!</b>

10:20.970 --> 10:23.720
<b>They say my intuition is rather accurate.</b>

10:23.720 --> 10:26.600
<b>I daresay you'll see the two of them soon.{lol}</b>

10:26.810 --> 10:28.140
<b>Miss Aria...</b>

10:32.730 --> 10:33.900
<b><i>I was lucky.</i></b>

10:33.900 --> 10:36.780
<b><i>In the end, I was saved by good people.</i></b>

10:37.570 --> 10:39.820
<b><i>Now it's just Sayo and Ieyasu.</i></b>

10:40.660 --> 10:43.990
<b><i>I hope they both made it to the capital safely.</i></b>

10:46.790 --> 10:48.870
<b>Next, let's visit the store across the road!</b>

10:48.870 --> 10:50.000
<b>Please wait, my lady!</b>

10:51.880 --> 10:54.590
<b>Her shopping trips aren't for the faint of heart, I see.</b>

10:55.380 --> 10:58.300
<b>The sheer volume is getting ridiculous.</b>

10:58.880 --> 11:00.550
<b>It's not just the young lady.</b>

11:00.550 --> 11:02.510
<b>All women are like this.</b>

11:02.850 --> 11:04.140
<b>Really?</b>

11:04.140 --> 11:07.270
<b>The ones I know have no trouble choosing clothes.</b>

11:07.270 --> 11:08.640
<b>It's not like I have anything else!</b>

11:08.640 --> 11:09.940
<b>But anyway, Tatsumi.</b>

11:09.940 --> 11:10.520
<b>Yes?</b>

11:10.520 --> 11:11.560
<b>Take a look at that.</b>

11:11.560 --> 11:12.350
<b>Huh?</b>

11:12.350 --> 11:16.610
<b>That building in the distance is the imperial palace. 
The heart of the capital.</b>

11:16.610 --> 11:18.320
<b>It's huge!</b>

11:18.530 --> 11:22.280
<b>Is that where the great emperor is? 
The one who holds the fate of nations in his hand?</b>

11:22.280 --> 11:23.120
<b>Not quite.</b>

11:23.120 --> 11:24.490
<b>It's a little different than that.</b>

11:26.160 --> 11:28.950
<b>There's an emperor, but he's only a child.</b>

11:29.660 --> 11:32.710
<b>The prime minister controls 
the emperor from the shadows.</b>

11:32.710 --> 11:34.840
<b>And he's why this country is rotting from the inside out.</b>

11:34.840 --> 11:35.590
<b>The pri—</b>

11:36.380 --> 11:38.130
<b>Don't say anything suspicious.</b>

11:38.130 --> 11:39.970
<b>If anyone hears us, they'll have our heads.</b>

11:41.470 --> 11:42.800
<b>Then...</b>

11:42.800 --> 11:45.390
<b>That's why my village suffers from such unbearable taxes?</b>

11:45.390 --> 11:46.760
<b>A mere fact of life in the capital.</b>

11:50.520 --> 11:52.650
<b>But there are also people like those.</b>

11:55.770 --> 11:57.070
<b>"Night Raid"?</b>

11:57.070 --> 12:00.780
<b>They're a group of assassins that have been terrorizing the imperial capital.</b>

12:00.780 --> 12:04.530
<b>As the name suggests, they attack 
their victims under cover of night.</b>

12:04.530 --> 12:08.540
<b>They mainly target high-ranking executives and the capital's upper class.</b>

12:08.910 --> 12:10.660
<b>Prepare yourself, just in case.</b>

12:10.660 --> 12:11.710
<b>Yes, sir.</b>

12:11.710 --> 12:15.000
<b>Also, could you lend a hand over there?</b>

12:15.000 --> 12:16.000
<b>Huh?</b>

12:16.960 --> 12:18.710
<b>What ordeal is this?!</b>

12:24.890 --> 12:25.970
<b>Now, then...</b>

12:25.970 --> 12:28.560
<b>Maybe I'll make another entry in my diary tonight.</b>

12:28.560 --> 12:30.810
<b>I just can't give up this hobby.</b>

12:33.350 --> 12:34.190
<b>Eh?</b>

12:46.240 --> 12:47.700
<b>My apologies.</b>

12:49.240 --> 12:50.240
<b>What's going on?</b>

12:50.870 --> 12:52.000
<b>Murderous intent?</b>

12:54.420 --> 12:55.420
<b><i>It can't be.</i></b>

13:01.170 --> 13:02.300
<b><i>That's...</i></b>

13:15.440 --> 13:16.900
<b><i>Night Raid!</i></b>

13:18.860 --> 13:20.440
<b>Night Raid...</b>

13:20.770 --> 13:23.190
<b>So you'd even target these people? Just because they're wealthy?</b>

13:24.650 --> 13:26.110
<b><i>What do I do?</i></b>

13:26.110 --> 13:27.610
<b><i>Do I assist the guards?</i></b>

13:27.610 --> 13:29.070
<b><i>Or defend the house?</i></b>

13:29.070 --> 13:32.080
<b>Your targets are the three guards, Akame.</b>

13:33.620 --> 13:34.870
<b>They will be eliminated.</b>

13:47.430 --> 13:49.930
<b>Listen. Don't let that sword of hers touch you.{seems like standard practice for swords...}</b>

14:01.150 --> 14:05.650
<b>A fitting end for someone like me, already rotting from within...{lol ok}</b>

14:06.360 --> 14:08.200
<b>What's with these guys?</b>

14:08.200 --> 14:09.200
<b>They're worse than monsters!</b>

14:11.990 --> 14:13.200
<b>How pathetic,</b>

14:13.200 --> 14:14.830
<b>turning tail at the sight of the enemy.</b>

14:14.830 --> 14:17.620
<b>Though, who wouldn't run in these circumstances?</b>

14:17.620 --> 14:20.710
<b><i>They were wiped out in an instant.</i></b>

14:20.710 --> 14:22.880
<b><i>At the very least, I must protect Miss Aria!</i></b>

14:24.380 --> 14:26.170
<b>H-Help!</b>

14:26.170 --> 14:28.430
<b>I have a daughter!</b>

14:28.430 --> 14:29.890
<b>Calm down.</b>

14:29.890 --> 14:31.350
<b>You'll see her soon in the next world.</b>

14:31.350 --> 14:33.220
<b>You'd murder even my daughter?</b>

14:33.220 --> 14:34.600
<b>Have you no mercy?</b>

14:34.600 --> 14:35.770
<b>Mercy?</b>

14:36.730 --> 14:37.940
<b>What's that?</b>

14:42.110 --> 14:44.440
<b>Hurry, my lady! This way!</b>

14:44.440 --> 14:45.440
<b>What's going on?</b>

14:45.440 --> 14:47.070
<b>We need to get to the storehouse!</b>

14:47.070 --> 14:48.320
<b>It'll be safe there!</b>

14:49.070 --> 14:50.070
<b>There you are!</b>

14:51.740 --> 14:52.950
<b>Tatsumi?</b>

14:54.700 --> 14:56.370
<b>You came at a good time.</b>

14:56.370 --> 14:59.290
<b>We will take shelter within the storehouse until the authorities arrive.</b>

14:59.290 --> 15:00.960
<b>You fend them off until then.</b>

15:01.580 --> 15:02.790
<b>That's impossible—</b>

15:06.590 --> 15:08.220
<b>I guess I have no choice!</b>

15:10.880 --> 15:12.050
<b>Not a target.</b>

15:15.890 --> 15:16.850
<b>Damn!</b>

15:17.850 --> 15:19.020
<b>Target.</b>

15:24.520 --> 15:25.520
<b><i>Eliminate.</i></b>

15:40.080 --> 15:41.040
<b>Eliminate.</b>

15:41.040 --> 15:42.330
<b>Hold it!</b>

15:44.460 --> 15:46.380
<b>You are not a target.</b>

15:46.380 --> 15:47.670
<b>There is no need to kill you.</b>

15:47.670 --> 15:50.170
<b>But you intend to kill this girl, don't you?</b>

15:50.170 --> 15:50.800
<b>Yep.</b>

15:50.800 --> 15:52.010
<b>"Yep"?!</b>

15:52.010 --> 15:53.680
<b>If you get in my way, I'll kill you.</b>

15:53.680 --> 15:55.600
<b>That doesn't mean I can just leave her!</b>

15:55.600 --> 15:56.560
<b>Is that so?</b>

15:56.930 --> 15:58.020
<b>Then I shall eliminate you.</b>

15:58.970 --> 16:01.190
<b>Ugh, what a mess.</b>

16:02.940 --> 16:07.070
<b><i>That's odd. Akame hasn't finished them off yet?</i></b>

16:07.070 --> 16:08.110
<b>Huh? Wait!</b>

16:08.110 --> 16:09.490
<b>Oh, man.</b>

16:09.860 --> 16:12.780
<b>How unlucky can one guy be?</b>

16:14.240 --> 16:17.990
<b><i>This isn't someone I can defeat in my current state.</i></b>

16:17.990 --> 16:20.950
<b><i>But I can't worry about that now.</i></b>

16:21.210 --> 16:23.710
<b><i>If I can't even save this one girl,</i></b>

16:23.710 --> 16:25.460
<b><i>then how will I save an entire village?</i></b>

16:33.380 --> 16:34.010
<b>Oh, crap!</b>

16:37.890 --> 16:38.970
<b>Tatsumi!</b>

16:46.900 --> 16:49.940
<b>I figured you'd take me for dead and come closer, but no.</b>

16:49.940 --> 16:52.150
<b>It didn't feel like I struck flesh.</b>

16:53.650 --> 16:55.820
<b>Looks like I was saved by my friends back home.</b>

16:57.660 --> 17:01.080
<b><i>He took a hit from Akame, and he's still standing.</i></b>

17:01.080 --> 17:02.700
<b><i>That kid's pretty good.</i></b>

17:04.410 --> 17:05.420
<b>Eliminate.</b>

17:06.330 --> 17:07.500
<b>Wait a second!</b>

17:07.500 --> 17:09.040
<b>Aren't you guys just here for their money?</b>

17:09.040 --> 17:10.630
<b>Let her go!</b>

17:10.630 --> 17:11.960
<b>This is no war!</b>

17:11.960 --> 17:14.220
<b>Why would you kill an innocent girl?</b>

17:14.680 --> 17:17.050
<b><i>It's no use. She isn't listening to anything I say!</i></b>

17:19.760 --> 17:20.680
<b>Hold it.</b>

17:22.470 --> 17:23.520
<b>What are you doing?</b>

17:23.520 --> 17:25.440
<b>We still have time, right?</b>

17:25.440 --> 17:27.770
<b>I kinda owe this kid a favor.</b>

17:27.770 --> 17:29.610
<b>Might as well repay it.</b>

17:31.940 --> 17:33.650
<b>You're those boobs from earlier!</b>

17:33.650 --> 17:35.780
<b>That's right! The beautiful lady!</b>

17:36.200 --> 17:37.240
<b>Young man.</b>

17:37.240 --> 17:41.080
<b>You said something about killing the innocent, didn't you?</b>

17:41.370 --> 17:44.500
<b>Will you be able to say the same thing after seeing this?</b>

17:47.960 --> 17:50.750
<b>Take a good look. This is what lies in the shadows of the imperial capital.</b>

17:53.880 --> 17:56.380
<b>Wh-What the hell is this?</b>

17:57.550 --> 18:01.140
<b>They lure people from the countryside with honeyed words,</b>

18:01.140 --> 18:05.020
<b>only to treat them as playthings and torture them to death.</b>

18:05.640 --> 18:07.730
<b>That's the true face of this household.</b>

18:10.190 --> 18:11.360
<b>Sayo...</b>

18:11.900 --> 18:14.190
<b>Hey, Sayo.</b>

18:14.190 --> 18:15.360
<b>Is that you, Sayo?</b>

18:15.360 --> 18:17.150
<b>Was that someone you knew?</b>

18:18.820 --> 18:19.870
<b>Hold on.</b>

18:20.570 --> 18:23.540
<b>I don't think you deserve to walk away after this, missy.</b>

18:23.540 --> 18:25.450
<b>The people of this household did this?</b>

18:25.450 --> 18:26.830
<b>That's right.</b>

18:26.830 --> 18:29.210
<b>And since the guards kept quiet, 
they were just as guilty.</b>

18:29.210 --> 18:30.080
<b>That's a lie!</b>

18:30.080 --> 18:32.170
<b>I didn't even know this place existed!</b>

18:32.540 --> 18:36.340
<b>Who will you believe? Your savior or these murderers?</b>

18:37.300 --> 18:38.760
<b>Tatsumi...</b>

18:39.550 --> 18:42.050
<b>It's you, right, Tatsumi?</b>

18:42.390 --> 18:43.470
<b>It's me.</b>

18:44.510 --> 18:46.770
<b>I-Ieyasu?</b>

18:46.770 --> 18:50.350
<b>That girl invited Sayo and me to her home.</b>

18:50.350 --> 18:52.810
<b>But after eating dinner, we lost consciousness.</b>

18:52.810 --> 18:55.320
<b>And when we came to, we were here.</b>

18:55.320 --> 18:59.450
<b>Th-That girl tortured Sayo to death!</b>

19:02.910 --> 19:04.660
<b>What's so wrong about that?!</b>

19:05.700 --> 19:09.120
<b>You're all worthless hicks from the country!</b>

19:09.120 --> 19:10.330
<b>You might as well be cattle!</b>

19:10.330 --> 19:12.750
<b>I should be free to do whatever I want to the lot of you!</b>

19:13.130 --> 19:14.210
<b>Not to mention, that woman...</b>

19:14.210 --> 19:16.710
<b>How dare that cow have the 
silky-smooth hair I'd always dreamed of,</b>

19:16.710 --> 19:18.630
<b>while I struggle with mine every day?!</b>

19:18.970 --> 19:21.430
<b>That's why I made sure she suffered as much as possible!</b>

19:21.430 --> 19:24.390
<b>She should be grateful anyone paid that much attention to her!</b>

19:24.390 --> 19:27.430
<b>A family of sadists, disguised as good Samaritans.</b>

19:28.480 --> 19:30.270
<b>Sorry to hold you up.</b>

19:30.270 --> 19:31.230
<b>Eliminate.</b>

19:31.230 --> 19:32.020
<b>Wait.</b>

19:32.690 --> 19:33.770
<b>Don't tell me...</b>

19:33.770 --> 19:34.940
<b>You still want to defend her?</b>

19:35.270 --> 19:36.070
<b>No.</b>

19:36.570 --> 19:38.110
<b>I'll kill her myself!{EDGE MASTER}{YYYYEEAAAAHHHHH}{as per fyurie request, nvm the blood, i just cut myself on this edge}</b>

19:53.790 --> 19:55.500
<b><i>I know he has plenty of reason to hate her now,</i></b>

19:55.500 --> 19:57.960
<b><i>but he killed her without the slightest hesitation.</i></b>

20:00.550 --> 20:02.340
<b>Nice one, Tatsumi!</b>

20:02.340 --> 20:03.680
<b>That's a load off my mind!</b>

20:05.220 --> 20:06.300
<b>Ieyasu!</b>

20:08.520 --> 20:09.470
<b>Ieyasu...</b>

20:09.470 --> 20:11.270
<b>It's the final stages of Lubora.</b>

20:11.730 --> 20:14.440
<b>The lady of the house enjoyed drugging her victims.</b>

20:14.440 --> 20:17.650
<b>She wrote about it in detail in her diary.</b>

20:17.980 --> 20:19.940
<b>He cannot be saved.</b>

20:20.780 --> 20:22.360
<b>Tatsumi...</b>

20:22.360 --> 20:23.070
<b>Ieyasu!</b>

20:23.360 --> 20:26.580
<b>Sayo... She never gave in to that bitch.</b>

20:26.580 --> 20:28.330
<b>She was so cool,</b>

20:29.080 --> 20:30.580
<b>even at the very end.</b>

20:31.080 --> 20:33.750
<b>That's why I, the great Ieyasu...</b>

20:33.750 --> 20:36.710
<b>will settle for no less...</b>

20:39.090 --> 20:42.050
<b>It seems he kept himself alive by willpower alone.</b>

20:43.630 --> 20:45.300
<b>What's wrong with this city?</b>

20:47.010 --> 20:47.550
<b>Let's go.</b>

20:47.850 --> 20:48.680
<b>Hey...</b>

20:49.260 --> 20:50.930
<b>Why don't we bring the kid with us?</b>

20:53.810 --> 20:56.270
<b>We can always use an extra hand at our hideout.</b>

20:54.350 --> 20:56.610
<b>What are you doing? Lemme go!</b>

20:56.270 --> 20:59.190
<b>He has luck, courage, and even skill! 
Wouldn't you agree?</b>

20:56.610 --> 20:59.980
<b>I have to give them a proper burial!</b>

20:59.520 --> 21:02.820
