21:06.280 --> 21:07.740
<b>What were you doing?</b>

21:07.740 --> 21:09.450
<b>And what is that thing?</b>

21:09.450 --> 21:10.240
<b>Our new friend!</b>

21:10.240 --> 21:11.160
<b>Huh?</b>

21:11.160 --> 21:13.210
<b>Oh? Didn't I tell you?</b>

21:14.080 --> 21:16.790
<b>From now on, you're one of us.</b>

21:17.290 --> 21:19.750
